<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="jumbotron text-center">
      <h1>Quiz Online Help</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container" >
      <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #007bff;">How do you set up a competition?</h2>
      <hr>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm">
          <p><b>1. The options of a competition.</b></p>
          <p>- Competition code: <b>Competition activation code.</b></p>
          <p>- Start date: <b> Time to begin the competition.</b></p>
          <p>- Finish date: <b> Time to end the competition.</b></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm">
          <p><b>2. Steps to create a ticket.</b></p>
          <p>- Step 1: Click <b><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> in page your ticket.</b></p>
          <p>- Step 2: Click <b>"Edit"</b></p>
          <p>- Step 3: Fill out the information ticket <b><i>"Competition code, Start date, Finish date".</i></b></p >
          <p>- Step 3: Click <b>"Update ticket".</b></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="help-btn">
      <p><%= link_to "Home", root_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %></p>
      <p><%= link_to "Back", help_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %></p>
    </div>
  </body>
  <style>
    .help-btn{
      display:flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .help-btn p {
      margin: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
    }
  </style>
